                    What is R?
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                    An <strong>open-source statistical programming language</strong> built for statistics, data wrangling, and graphics. Originating at the University of Auckland (1993) and now stewarded by the R Core Team, it has over <strong>20,000+ CRAN packages</strong> and strong community support.
                </p>
