                    </svg>
                    Why use R in this module?
                </h2>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 list-disc list-inside">
                    <li><strong>Rich statistical libraries</strong> for time-series, econometrics, and ML.</li>
                    <li><strong>Clean and consistent Tidyverse syntax</strong> for both EDA and large-scale pipelines.</li>
                    <li>Native plotting (<strong>ggplot2</strong>) for publication-quality visuals.</li>
                    <li>Supports <strong>reproducible workflows</strong> with Quarto and Shiny.</li>
